[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 1.5,
    "text": "As you know, the holidays are here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.51,
    "endTime": 3.1,
    "text": "The other day, I saw this in the news."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.2,
    "endTime": 6.550000000000001,
    "text": "Amazon just released an Alexa compatible Christmas tree."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.6,
    "endTime": 9.0,
    "text": "It costs $299."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.0,
    "endTime": 11.6,
    "text": "You can control the lights by talking to Alexa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.61,
    "endTime": 13.7,
    "text": "I can't believe they're doing that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.8,
    "endTime": 15.0,
    "text": "I can't believe I bought one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.3,
    "endTime": 17.3,
    "text": "Bring it out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.3,
    "endTime": 29.0,
    "text": "Thank you, Andy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.0,
    "endTime": 31.5,
    "text": "Let's see if it works."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.6,
    "endTime": 33.5,
    "text": "Alexa, turn on tree lights."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.51,
    "endTime": 34.3,
    "text": "Sure, Ellen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.4,
    "endTime": 36.5,
    "text": "Turning lights on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.5,
    "endTime": 38.6,
    "text": "Oh, it's amazing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.6,
    "endTime": 39.2,
    "text": "That's very cool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.21,
    "endTime": 41.4,
    "text": "Alexa, can you make the lights blink?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.5,
    "endTime": 43.0,
    "text": "No problem, Ellen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.3,
    "endTime": 46.0,
    "text": "We wish you a Merry Christmas."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.1,
    "endTime": 47.1,
    "text": "We wish you--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.1,
    "endTime": 48.2,
    "text": "- I didn't ask you - Wish, wish, wish."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.2,
    "endTime": 50.6,
    "text": "I didn't-- stop."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.6,
    "endTime": 52.0,
    "text": "Wish, wish, wish."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.2,
    "endTime": 55.0,
    "text": "I didn't ask you to sing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.1,
    "endTime": 56.0,
    "text": "What a Grinch."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.0,
    "endTime": 58.7,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.7,
    "endTime": 59.5,
    "text": "Well, this is great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.5,
    "endTime": 64.0,
    "text": "But not everybody celebrates Christmas, so I'm coming out with the first smart menorah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.0,
    "endTime": 65.0,
    "text": "Look at that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.0,
    "endTime": 73.7,
    "text": "This is Morty the menorah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.71,
    "endTime": 77.39999999999999,
    "text": "Morty is just like Alexa, but he can also help with your Hanukkah traditions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.4,
    "endTime": 78.60000000000001,
    "text": "Isn't that right, Morty?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.7,
    "endTime": 79.7,
    "text": "That's right, Ellen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.8,
    "endTime": 83.0,
    "text": "Would you like me to make a reservation for dinner Christmas day?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.1,
    "endTime": 87.0,
    "text": "There are five Chinese restaurants in your area."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.3,
    "endTime": 88.44,
    "text": "No, no, no thanks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.5,
    "endTime": 89.3,
    "text": "But look what else."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.31,
    "endTime": 91.2,
    "text": "Morty, light the menorah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.3,
    "endTime": 92.39999999999999,
    "text": "Ellen, I can't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.5,
    "endTime": 94.0,
    "text": "It's not Hanukkah yet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.5,
    "endTime": 96.0,
    "text": "When is Hanukkah?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.1,
    "endTime": 99.1,
    "text": "It starts Sunday, December 22nd."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.1,
    "endTime": 99.5,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.6,
    "endTime": 100.1,
    "text": "Thanks, Morty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.2,
    "endTime": 102.0,
    "text": "How do you spell Hanukkah?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.1,
    "endTime": 108.3,
    "text": "C-H-A-N-- Alexa, how do you spell Hanukkah?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.5,
    "endTime": 115.0,
    "text": "Hanukkah is spelled H-A-N-N?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.0,
    "endTime": 119.0,
    "text": "Morty, let's spell it together."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.1,
    "endTime": 125.0,
    "text": "C, H, A, N, Q, S."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.0,
    "endTime": 128.0,
    "text": "4, L."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.3,
    "endTime": 127.0,
    "text": "Hyphen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.0,
    "endTime": 128.0,
    "text": "L, L."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.1,
    "endTime": 128.79999999999998,
    "text": "X."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.0,
    "endTime": 130.2,
    "text": "The number three."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.2,
    "endTime": 132.5,
    "text": "5, hashtag, 2."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.5,
    "endTime": 133.2,
    "text": "You know what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.2,
    "endTime": 134.0,
    "text": "- R - A car."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.1,
    "endTime": 135.2,
    "text": "You guys, hey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.21,
    "endTime": 135.6,
    "text": "That's OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.61,
    "endTime": 136.3,
    "text": "I'm sorry I asked."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.4,
    "endTime": 138.0,
    "text": "Just take a break, okay?."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.1,
    "endTime": 140.6,
    "text": "I have some exciting news for all my viewers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.61,
    "endTime": 143.5,
    "text": "I am looking for elves to help me with my 12 Days of Giveaways."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.51,
    "endTime": 148.0,
    "text": "All you have to do is send me a short video telling me why you'd make a fantastic elf."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.1,
    "endTime": 150.5,
    "text": "If I pick you, you'll join my elite elf crew."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.51,
    "endTime": 153.0,
    "text": "We have had some big names serve as elves."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.1,
    "endTime": 155.29999999999998,
    "text": "We've had Jeff Garland."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.3,
    "endTime": 157.0,
    "text": "And we have had Andy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.0,
    "endTime": 160.0,
    "text": "I guess that's it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.7,
    "endTime": 165.0,
    "text": "So upload your video to Ellentube with the title Ellen's Little Helper."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.1,
    "endTime": 166.0,
    "text": "We'll be back."
  }
]